<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201004/23228e4b502940f9af1aeca5a77e1f0b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201004/998c032742a042aaaf14d18a2718d975.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201004/ddc1788fb03d42019f59efe6891ac6b5.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">除了交警部门的火眼金睛</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">咱毕节的小伙伴的举报</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">也是相当给力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201004/0cb43eddf1774747b015564e793d2af8.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201004/2dc6c81acd9f44f7807343734f284e64.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201004/030773f4948f4d96a87c1966d984a0f9.png" max-width="600" /></p>
